{{version030}}
{{flavour|Summons a temporary mirror image of an enemy. Such a copy has the same physical prowess as the original, and can cast the same spells.}}
'''Summon Illusion''' is a monster-only spell which [[summon]]s an exact copy of the target, friendly to the caster. If used on the player, it will create a [[player ghost]] based on your current stats. Like other summons, it is vulnerable to [[Abjuration]] and [[Yara's Violent Unravelling]].

